STILU is a family of sans serif typefaces. In this package are four weights avalaible: Light, Regular, SemiBold and Bold plus obliques. OpenType features: ligatures, small caps, small caps figures, old style figures, proportional lining and tabular lining figures.

This font is free for personal and commercial uses. Donations are highly appreciated.

This Font Software is licensed under the SIL Open Font License, Version 1.1.
This license is available with a FAQ at:
